● Good question to understand before you commit to anything. Here's how it works:                                                                                                                               
   
  ---                                                                                                                                                                                                           
  The Basic Flow                                                                                                                                                                                                
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
  You write code locally → push to GitHub → hosting platform picks it up → serves it to visitors
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
  Your domain name just points to wherever your site is hosted. That's it.                                                                                                                                      
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
  ---                                                                                                                                                                                                           
  Where the Code Lives
                      
  GitHub is where you store and version your code. Free, industry standard, and every hosting platform connects to it. Think of it as the source of truth — you make changes locally, push to GitHub, and the
  site updates automatically.                                                                                                                                                                                   
   
  ---                                                                                                                                                                                                           
  Hosting Options (Where It Actually Runs)
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
  Vercel — what I'd recommend for this project
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
  - Free tier is genuinely generous (more than enough for a personal art site)
  - Connects directly to GitHub — push code, site updates in seconds                                                                                                                                            
  - Handles everything automatically (SSL certificate, CDN, fast global delivery)                                                                                                                               
  - Built for exactly this kind of modern static/dynamic site                                                                                                                                                   
  - No server management on your part                                                                                                                                                                           
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
  Netlify                                                                                                                                                                                                       
   
  - Nearly identical to Vercel, also free tier                                                                                                                                                                  
  - Either works fine — this is largely personal preference
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
  GitHub Pages
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
  - Free, but limited — static sites only, no backend logic                                                                                                                                                     
  - Fine for a pure portfolio, not ideal once you add Stripe/payments
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
  VPS (DigitalOcean, Linode, etc.)                                                                                                                                                                              
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
  - You rent an actual server ($5-6/mo)                                                                                                                                                                         
  - Full control but you manage everything — updates, security, uptime
  - Overkill for this project, unnecessary complexity                                                                                                                                                           
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
  ---                                                                                                                                                                                                           
  What "No Server Management" Actually Means on Vercel                                                                                                                                                          
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
  With Vercel you never:
  - SSH into a machine                                                                                                                                                                                          
  - Worry about uptime or crashes                                                                                                                                                                               
  - Configure web servers (nginx etc.)
  - Manage SSL renewals                                                                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
  You just write code and push. They handle the infrastructure.
                                                                                                                                                                                                                
